{"tid":959562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鐘意飲台式飲品嘅你，係咪忘記咗台灣塑化劑事件？？？","createTime":"2018-12-28T16:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T03:02:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1371cc7db9eca717bd2487154cf878efb94eb87e","tid":959562,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"呢件事係直接証明咗台灣人係繁體支那<br />\n<br />\n盛極而衰　台灣塑化劑事件擊破泡沫<br />\n<br />\n97金融風暴爆破後，香港經濟環境轉差，消費力轉弱，但因為租金仍較合理，因此生意有條件守下去，但2003年沙士過後，自由行政策的開放，令租金大幅飆升，為仙跡岩的生意帶來極大打擊。主打休閒概念的仙跡岩，因為翻桌率低，不斷加租令加盟商經營壓力越益沉重，直至2011年台灣爆發塑化劑事件，不少製作台式茶飲的原料被發現含有塑化劑，香港人最少半年不敢飲珍珠奶茶，台式茶飲店舖亦大量倒閉。"},{"pid":"f028d3b05275c0bfb50e2d8e0a1b536a156f85fd","tid":959562,"uid":123456,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"港豬<br />\n豬係餵咩都食㗎啦"},{"pid":"64b917ef6a1ff09c9fe25ab63eda02d1b4e894b1","tid":959562,"uid":104658,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"香港人總是善忘  新聞過幾日已經冇人記得"},{"pid":"841b3b7d614eb6dda39379b0b02cf0e5c678e3ed","tid":959562,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:59:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74ce2ef1fe4b2ac48c50f7902b0f01ce304f191b","tid":959562,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"連喜茶都飲<br />\n重有乜嘢係唔飲?"},{"pid":"4df0cd6304f5a1a48eba017c092ba049f24c4e15","tid":959562,"uid":19066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:10:48.000Z","msg":"台灣的風景是狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3d76ff880ea18221361229612aa85646a2bac7","tid":959562,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T00:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2397b830b5e455d4e416d5f9664ed5b9bbd6292a","tid":959562,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:02:40.000Z","msg":"以前有個同學讀中學